{"tid":2102964,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港你去過幾多地方？","createTime":"2020-07-11T01:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T09:09:27.000Z","uid":104804,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"50662e7ba781343c1860ff1be2a767094e1be291","tid":2102964,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:20:30.000Z","msg":"我係窮毒撚<br />\n離島只去過長洲塔門<br />\n好多地方都係中小學旅行先去過<br />\n好似天水圍濕地公園嘉道理農場咁<br />\n香港仔馬灣愉景灣都係返工先去過一次<br />\n咩野薄扶林清水灣淺水灣石澳都未去過<br />\n好出名流浮山都未去過<br />\n仲有好多好多真係講出黎都比人笑<br />\n<br />\n娛樂方面<br />\n迪士尼未去過<br />\n海洋公園去過三次(兩次學校一次生日免費)<br />\n<br />\nneway去過一次朋友請<br />\nredmr去過一次自費<br />\n<br />\n去戲院睇電影都應該有十幾次<br />\n蘭柱坊一次都未去過"},{"pid":"f0a047c0bdb9e3dc9a83076b5ddfbefedd1d53f4","tid":2102964,"uid":49977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:23:32.000Z","msg":"幾歲？住邊？學歷？"},{"pid":"2ae3b90c10edf78767abbac7d762bb4a29b69487","tid":2102964,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f0a047c0bdb9e3dc9a83076b5ddfbefedd1d53f4","tid":2102964,"uid":49977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:23:32.000Z","msg":"幾歲？住邊？學歷？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"三十歲住沙田ive公屋佬<br />\n平時娛樂都係屋企對住電腦<br />\n砌好部機只係比電費上網費就得"},{"pid":"66216241ca1e80bbb82d51d1c3af0ff334074998","tid":2102964,"uid":185092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:36:21.000Z","msg":"離島我剩係去過長洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5de9411e5f090742b701bd81c4c78a48bc1cf1b","tid":2102964,"uid":186755,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"蘭柱坊我廿到尾都未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac02865710cd6a63780b61097476be1fa9bed3ff","tid":2102964,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T02:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset